Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,635区check OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0500开始会有磁气风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计三天后消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量护罩移至2及3区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全方位一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座标系统，检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日看来也风平浪静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没什么人会来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是份无聊轻松的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那也只剩一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！终于也可以和这个沉闷的警卫太空站道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间也令你很寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到卫星工作后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便跟你生个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有物体接近，它会和太空站相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…海盗船！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，今日的GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来源自五年前的这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事怎会和多蒙扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，他能否找到和Devil Gundam一起飞落地球的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京二的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看他和今日的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Canada Lumber Gundam的比赛结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}报仇！复仇的宇宙刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到尼亚瓜拉大瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欣赏一下风景总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标只是neo Canada的GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并非来观光的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样说是什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见你很累，想你轻松一下罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，我不会再跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，你既然想那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，对我来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我也是为你着想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌！我和你到此为止！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！你要做得到便试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是自愿做你的拍档的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是neo Japan的多蒙·卡休吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫安东尼·格拉汉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Canada的Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥会来这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Russia的人被你击败后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了战略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采用主动把敌人击倒的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们第一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们neo Canada
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，你想跟我一起合力击倒neo Russia吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你告诉我Bolt Gundam的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，来这里找你的我们是笨蛋吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我的目标只是neo Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束后我把我GUNDAM的头给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样，你会同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干吗开动GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击，Lumber Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是neo Canada的GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，跟我比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT，READY…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才已经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没打算和你正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Bolt Gundam的情报告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力很惊人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King of Heart 多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会因为这点攻击便死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是多蒙的拍档吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯告诉我Bolt Gundam的情报时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就来洛矶山脉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，这女人由我看管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉…莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Japan的多蒙·卡休来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，他昨日在尼亚瓜拉大瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和neo Canada进行了非正式的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道那男人会有何行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令进入一级警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那严重了一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来打算吓你们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是手重了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥，捉住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦～你看来不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？阿鲁哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在监狱令动作迟钝了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那样才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼·格拉汉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对手的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，虽然我不知道内情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他看来跟你们有深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了准备和他再次比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是用阿鲁哥来试招吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜，因为没多少人像格拉汉那样力大无穷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你的拍档莉茵也被捉去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她绝交了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你那么粗暴，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我想你多留一会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟有什么目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手杀死阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀…杀死他…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，根据FIGHT的国际条约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是比赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是审判
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，他杀了我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙以前是刑警？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，因为某件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他辞去了宇宙警察的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用毕生的时间追捕某男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前宇宙海盗阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，已经是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉汉和妻子诺玛两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时在警卫太空站工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且工作会在一星期后结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但阿鲁哥的海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞向两人的太空站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛！加油！别放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人拼命求生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼！！\N诺玛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，就在那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名男子来到两人的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来，我幸运的被前来巡逻的警卫舰队救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我醒来后看见的太空站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经毁烂不堪，只剩一堆岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里已经空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，妻子的惨况深深印在我眼内，挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，杀死我妻子的那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会捉到他，为妻子报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来，我听说他被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为neo Russia的Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲手审判他的时候来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你不惜成为Gundam Fighter…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他成为Fighter，我没其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没用，自己回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想杀死阿鲁哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么理由也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接攻击对方战士是犯规的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，会犯上杀人罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做，你妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用完我就这样算了，太过份了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇鬼现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休也是个正直的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，两人夹攻我也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，为了多谢你们带我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遵守诺言首先跟他战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和还生存的一方比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是你们喜欢的高效率战术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥在海盗时代不会取人性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且是毫无反抗能力的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么！？你违抗命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把GUNDAM停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能轻松一下的好像是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我等了这一日多久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像来势汹汹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我要为妻子报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能眼睁睁的看着你杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！改变主意！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是互相杀戮！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？莉茵在里面！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做，你妻子没理由会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！根本解决不了问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子…也和你一样仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，阿鲁哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场战斗，停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别阻住我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就要为诺玛报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你要帮阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也就是我的敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自以为是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也准备了新的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你是基于礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这只手在闪耀和咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在叫我打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正犯规攻击驾驶舱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，这并非正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！你还生存吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我，我现在来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分胜负吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…竟然弄成这样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看来也对你们做出当年阿鲁哥所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去，哪一方赢也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只是愤怒和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我是个蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥！住手！住手呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵还在里面的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分！住手！我求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是格拉汉你还不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把Shining Gundam的头给你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…你…你帮我救救莉茵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥，和当时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样，憎恨你的人就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，你今后能高枕无忧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，动手吧，杀死我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么！？你为什么救我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁哥·加鲁斯基！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！？阿鲁哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放过我，我会永远追杀你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:20:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我讲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本国刚刚送来当时的报告书你先看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当日，逼阿鲁哥的船飞向你的太空站的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是联邦警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果引致那场意外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那是意外！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿鲁哥当时并非想杀死你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说阿鲁哥当时想救诺玛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会忘记当日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事实是怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终是连累死了你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，你想报仇的便来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会在今届擂台战胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救出被囚的同伴前继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，我不逃也不会躲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…会追杀阿鲁哥直到决赛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否为复仇的心画上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，逝去的幸福不会再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面谁都一样

Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:32.14,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便数千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.53,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:40.97,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨着 追求着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:44.54,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:51.69,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人啊 在我瞳孔的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:57.39,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实摇曳着的真实
